com.kinvey
Class KinveySettings

java.lang.Object
  com.kinvey.KinveySettings

public class KinveySettings
extends Object

Finds the configuration file kinvey.properties located on the classpath of the android application

Usually this file is located in assets/kinvey.properties

loadFromProperties

protected void loadFromProperties(Context ctx,
                                  String propFilename)
Loads the properties with the context given.

If ctx is null the properties file path returned by AbstractSettings.getDefaultPropertiesFilename() method is called on ClassLoader.getResource(String)

Parameters:
ctx - the application context
propFilename - the file name of the properties file (i.e. "kinvey.properties")
